Cases






                                        Peter has won multiple six and seven-figure Awards and settlements on behalf of his clients. Recently he settled a business litigation case for $3,000,000.00. On a smaller scale but equally important to his client was a police misconduct case against the City of Henderson which settled for $70,000.00 involving a police officer pushing his client against a car.
                    





